        <abstract>
            <p>Book finished some two weeks.</p>
            <p>Feeling much better at Ilkley.</p>
            <p>Lyell thinks favourably of book but "staggered" at lengths to which CD goes.</p>
            <p>Which continental botanists should receive presentation copies?</p>
